处理涉未成年人网暴举报。 三、严防网暴信息传播扩散 1. 加强评论环节管理。 中央网信办印发《关于切实加强网络暴力治理的通知》- 中共中央网络安全和信息化委员会办公室"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx1.zhimg.com/80/v2-7c089dd3edeffc09f8095d3297561dde_720w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "43 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/564655069"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Iw++Nq9Hx5Jd6EAMaCDg3NzYwOTYwIOXuk5sGMAI4hgFAG3IJNTY0NjU1MDY5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "28_1667596126.0917954", "card_id": "Q_564661521", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 40}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "有一个特别节省的老妈是一种怎样的体验？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "41 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/564661521"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4Iw++Nq9Hx5Jd6EAMaCDg3NzYyMzkwIOCPlJsGMAA4RUAccgk1NjQ2NjE1MjF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "29_1667596126.0921576", "card_id": "Q_564594333", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 381}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "泽连斯基称若普京参加 G20 峰会，乌方不会出席，释放哪些信息？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "综合外媒报道，当地时间 11 月 3 日，乌克兰总统泽连斯基表示，如果俄罗斯总统普京出席二十国集团 (G20) 峰会，乌克兰就不会参加。 G20 峰会将于 11 月中旬在印度尼西亚巴厘岛举行。泽连斯基和普京都被邀请参会，但两国并未明确表示其领导人是否参加。 印尼总统佐科 11 月 2 日在雅加达透露，已有 17 个国家领导人确认参加峰会，普京曾于 10 月底表示，不排除亲自前往印尼参加 G20 峰会的可能性，他正在考虑。泽连斯基：若普京参加 G20 峰会，乌方不会出席 - 中新网"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx1.zhimg.com/80/v2-bfa313b9cdee3be41b1cb2c74f07504c_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "39 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/564594333"}}, 